quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa miim"
  41,2,"(Woto) Yaa sẽn sik n yi Rahmaan Naab nengẽ n yaa yolsg naaba."
  41,3,"Yaa gaf b sẽn wels a Aayayã, tɩ yaa Alkʋrãan sẽn ya laarabiimdu, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ nebã na bãnge."
  41,4,"N ya sũ-noogd la busgda, la b wʋsgã fãa gũda b kuidg n pa wʋmdẽ ye."
  41,5,"La b yeeele: ""tõnd sũyã bee lim pʋsẽ n yi bũmb ning fo sẽn boond tõnd n tʋgdẽ wã, tõnd tʋbẽ wã me kɩd n be beenẽ, tõnd ne foom sʋka gɩdr n be be. Bɩ f tʋm tɩ tõnd me tʋmdame""."
  41,6,"Yeele: ""ad mam yaa yĩng soab wala yãmba, tɩ b tʋm tɩ wat mam nengẽ: ""tɩ yãmb Soabã yaa Sob-yend tãa, bɩ y tẽeg tɩrg n tʋg A nengẽ la y kos-A yaafa. La wɩɩbd be ne lagem-n-taar rãmba."
  41,7,"(Lagem-n-taar rãmbã la) Nins sẽn pa kõt Zakã, bãmb leb n yaa kɩɩsdb ne laahrã,"
  41,8,"Ad neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd la b tʋm sẽn sõmbã, b tara keoor sẽn pa wãagde."
  41,9,"Yeele: ""Rẽ yĩnga yãmb na kɩfl ne Soab ning sẽn naan-a tẽngã rasem a yiib pʋgẽ, la y maan mak-n-taas ne-A, ad Yẽ la bõn-naandsã Soaba."
  41,10,"La A maan tãms sẽn yɑɑ bεd a zugu, la A ning bark a pʋgẽ, la A kord a rɩ-rãmb a pʋgẽ; tɩ wã yɩɩ rasem a naas sẽn zems taab pʋgẽ, (woto yaa leokre) sokdbã yĩnga."
  41,11,"Rẽ poorẽ t'A togl saagẽ wã t'a yaa wulwuku, t'A yeel-a ne tẽngã fãa: ""wa-y-yã, ne sak-n-tũ ma ne tɩlae"". Tɩ b yiibã yeele: ""tõnd waame tɩ d yaa sak-n-tũ rãmba"""
  41,12,"N maan b saas a yopoe rasem a yiib pʋgẽ, la A tʋms saag fãa pʋgẽ a tʋʋmã, la Tõnd faasa dũni saagã ne fɩtl-rãmba (ãdse) la b le yɑɑ gũudum, wãnde yaa a wilb Naab kordogo, Yẽ la a Mitã."
  41,13,"La b sã n balle, bɩ f yeele: ""M beoond-y lame ne halkr wala a Aad ne Samuud halkrã,"
  41,14,"Wakat ning tẽn-tʋʋmbã sẽn wa n wa b nengẽ b nens taoore la b nense poorẽ n yet-ba: ""ra tũ-y tɩ sã n pa Wẽnd ye"". La b yeel yã: ""tõnd Soabã sã n da tʋllẽ, A a sikdẽ-la Malεgse. Rẽnd tõnd yaa kɩfr-rãmb ne bũmb ning b sẽn tʋms ne yãmbã""."
  41,15,"La sã n yɑɑ ne a Aade, b waooga b mens tẽngã zug tɩ pa yɩ ne sɩd ye, la b yeele: ""ãnd pãng keelem n yɩɩd tõndo?"" Rẽ yĩngã b pa bãng tɩ ad Wẽnd ning sẽn naan-a bãmbã, Yẽ pãng keelem n yɩɩd bãmba? La b ra yɩɩme n kɩɩsd Tõnd yel-soalmã."
  41,16,"Tɩ Tõnd tʋms b zug seb-fubdgɑ zu-be-rasem rãmb pʋsẽ, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ d na leems-b yãnd naong dũni wã vɩɩm pʋga, la ad laahrã naong yãnd n yɩɩde, la b pa na n sõng-b ye."
  41,17,"La sã n ya ne a Samuud, Tõnd kãndg-b lame, tɩ b bʋ zondlem nonglem n yɩɩg kãndgre ( tũusa meneng n bas kãndgre) tɩ naon-faagdgã vũbgrã rɩk-ba b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmd bũmb ningã yĩnga."
  41,18,"La D tɩlg neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã, la b ra yɩ n zoet Wẽndã."
  41,19,"La raar ning b sẽn tigimd Wẽnd bεεbã n tʋg Bugmẽ wã tɩ b tardã,"
  41,20,"Hal tɩ b sã n wa ta-a, b tʋbã la b ninã la b gãndã maanda kaset b zug ne bũmb ning b sẽn yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  41,21,"Tɩ b yeel b gãndã: ""yaa bõe tɩ yãmb seet tõnd zugu?"". Tɩ b yeele : "" Wẽnd n kɩt tɩ tõnd gome, Soab ning sẽn kɩt-a tɩ bũmbã fãa gomã, la Yẽ n naan yãmb rẽenem, la b na n lebsa yãmb n tʋg A nengẽ""."
  41,22,"La yãmb ra pa yɩ n yɑeesdẽ n solgd tɩ y tʋbã la y ninã la y gãndã rɑ wɑ mɑɑne-y kaset ye, la ad yãmb ra tẽedame tɩ Wẽnd pa mi yãmb sẽn tʋmdã wʋsg fãa ye."
  41,23,"La yãmb tẽeb ning yãmb sẽn tẽ ne y Soabã halka yãmba, tɩ yãmb lebg bõn rãmba."
  41,24,"La b sã n maan sugri, rẽnd yaa Bugumã la b gãag zĩiga, b sã n baood padenga, bãmb pa yɩ b sẽn na n reeg-b rãmb padeng ye."
  41,25,"Tɩ Tõnd sεglg tũud-n-taas n kõ-ba, tɩ b faas ne-b bũmb ning sẽn be b neng taoore la sẽn be b poorẽ, tɩ gomdã sɩdg bãmb zugu, tɩ b kẽ n naag zãma sẽn reng bãmb taoor n yaa zĩn-dãmb la ninsaalba; ɑd b yɑɑ bõn rãmba."
  41,26,"La neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã yeelame: ""Ra kelg-y Alkʋrãan kãngã ye, la y maan bʋʋr a pʋgẽ, sãnde yãmb na wili"""
  41,27,"La D na leems neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã naong sẽn keeme, la D rol-b wẽng sẽn yɩɩd bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  41,28,"Woto bala, tɩ Wẽnd bεεbã rolb yaa Bugum. Bãmb tara paab zak a pʋgẽ tɩ yaa rolbo, b sẽn da yɩ n kɩɩsd Tõnd yel-soalmã yĩnga."
  41,29,"Tɩ neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã yeele:""yaa tõnd Soaba! wilg tõnd b yiib nins sẽn menes-b tõndã sẽn yi zĩn-dãmbẽ la ninsaalbẽ, tɩ d ning b yiibã tõnd nao-sɩlpamã tẽngre, sẽn na yɩl tɩ b zĩnd tẽngre""."
  41,30,"Neb nins sẽn yeele: ""tõnd soab la Wẽnde"". Rẽ poorẽ tɩ b tẽeg tɩrgã, malεgsã sigda b nengẽ (n yetẽ): ra yaεεs-y ye, ra sãam-y y sũur ye; noog-y y sũur ne Arzãn ning b sẽn da yɩ n pʋlem yãmbã."
  41,31,"Tõnd la yãmb lalldba, dũni vɩɩmã pʋgẽ la laahre, la yãmb tara a pʋgẽ bũmb ning yãmb yõyã sẽn maan yamleoog ne, yãmb leb n tara a pʋgẽ bũmb ning yãmb sẽn baoode""."
  41,32,"Tɩ yaa sãand sigb zĩig sẽn yi Yaafg Naabã nengẽ, Yolsg Naabã."
  41,33,"Ãnda koεεg manegr n yɩɩd ned ning sẽn bool-a n tʋg Wẽnd nengẽ, n tʋm sẽn sõmbe, la a yeele: ""ad mam lagma (sɑk-n-tũ-rãmbã) moeembã"" ?"
  41,34,"La tʋʋm-sõng la tʋʋm-wẽng pa makd taab ye. Bɩ f rol ne bũmb ning sẽn yɩɩd sõmblem, tɩ mikdame tɩ ned ning foom ne a sʋk beem sẽn da be wã, ɑ lebgda wa lall-n-ta-kεgenga."
  41,35,"La ned ka paamd woto ralla sẽn maan-b sugrã, la ned ka paamd-a ralla zu-noog soaba."
  41,36,"A Sʋɩtãan sã n wa tõg foom tõgb ninga, bɩ f kos gũudum ne Wẽnde, ad Yẽ la wʋmb Naab n yɑɑ Mita."
  41,37,"La sẽn leb n be A yel-soalmã pʋgẽ, yaa yʋngã la wĩndgã, la wĩntoogã la kiuugã, ra maan-y wĩntoogã suguud ye, ra maan-y kiuugã me ye, maan-y suguud Wẽnd yĩng bala, Soab ning sẽn naan-a bãmbã, tɩ y sã n yɩɩme tɩ yaa Yẽnda bal la y tũuda"
  41,38,"La b sã n waoog b mensã, rẽnd rãmb nins sẽn be fo Soabã nengẽ wã, b yɩlgd-A lame yʋng la wĩndga, tɩ b yam pa yit ye."
  41,39,"La sẽn leb n be A yel-soalmã pʋgẽ, yɑɑ fo sẽn ne tẽngã t'a yaa sẽn kʋɩ, tɩ Tõnd sã n sik koom a zug la a sẽn pus n fugumdi, ad soab ning sẽn vʋʋg-a wã, hakɩɩka A yaa kũ-rãmb vʋʋgda, ad A yaa tõogd ne bũmbã fãa gilli."
  41,40,"Ad neb nins sẽn golemd Tõnd Aayay wã pʋgẽ wã, b pa solg (ne) Tõnd ye, rẽ yĩngã b sẽn lobd-a soab Bugmẽ n yɩɩd sõmblem bɩ? Bɩ yaa ned ning sẽn wat ne bas-m-yam dũni yikr raarã, tʋm-y y sẽn rate, ad A yaa Net ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tʋmdã."
  41,41,"Neb nins sẽn kɩfl ne Tẽegrã (Alkʋrãɑnɑ) a sẽn wa n wɑ b nengẽ wã (b tɑrɑ nɑng yikrã rɑɑre), la ad a yaa gaf sẽn yaa zɩsgo."
  41,42,"Zĩrimbeed pa wat a pʋgẽ ye, pa wat a taoore, ka wat a poore; yaa sẽn sig n yi bʋʋd Mit nengẽ n yaa pẽgr Naaba."
  41,43,"B pa yet foom ralla bũmb ning sẽn da yeel tẽn-tʋʋmb sẽn reng fo taoore, ad fo Soabã yaa yaafg naaba, n leb n yaa nams-zabdg Soaba."
  41,44,"La Tõnd sã n da maan-a t'a yaa Alkʋrãan sẽn pa Laarabiindu, b rag n na yeele: ""yaa bõe yĩng tɩ b ka nɑ n wels a Aayayã (Alkʋrãan), rẽ yĩngã Kʋrãɑnɑ nɑ yi bu-zẽngɑ tɩ tẽn-tʋʋmã yaool n yaa laarba? Yeele: ""a yaa kãndgr la tɩp-tɩɩm ne neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã''. La neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩdã, kɩd n be b tʋbẽ wã, t'a yaa zondlem ne-ba, bãmb rãmbã, yɑɑ wɑlɑ b sẽn boond-b rãmb zĩig sẽn zãrẽ."
  41,45,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd kõo a Muusa Gafã, tɩ b kɩɩs taab a pʋgẽ, la sã n ka fo Soabã gomd sẽn reng taoor t'ɑ kõ n hɑlk-b yĩnga, b rag na n bʋ b sʋkã ne hɑlkre, ad bãmbã bee sik wʋsg pʋgẽ ne Alkʋrãɑna."
  41,46,"Ned ning sẽn tʋm-a sẽn sõmbe yaa a meng yĩnga, la ned ning sẽn wẽng-a be ne-a, f Soabã pa yɩ n yaa wẽgd baɑ bilfu ne A yembsã ye."
  41,47,"Dũni wã yikr minim lebsda Yẽ nengẽ. Tɩ-bil fãa pa yit a paokẽ, yãang fãa pa zãad pʋgɑ bɩ a rogɑ me, rẽnda ne A minim. Lɑ tẽeg-b raar ning A sẽn na n bool-b n yetẽ: ""Mam lagem-n-taasã bε?"" La b na n yeele : ""tõnd reegɑ d zugẽ, tɩ kaset soab ka be tõnd sʋkã n yetẽ tɩ Fo tɑrɑ lɑgem-n-tɑɑg ye""."
  41,48,"Tɩ bũmb ning b sẽn da yɩ n boond hal pĩndã menem n bas-ba, tɩ b bãng n wãag tɩ bãmb pa tar zoees zĩig ye."
  41,49,"Ninsaal yam pa yit sẽn sõmb kosg ye; la wẽng sã n paam-a, a yaa tẽeb-wãagdɑ n lak a yam."
  41,50,"La Tõnd sã n lɛεms-a yolsg sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ, keelem sẽn paam-a poorẽ, la ɑ sẽn yete : ""yãoã somba ne maam, la m pa tẽed tɩ Dũni wã na n yikame ye; b sã n lebs maam m Soabã nengẽ me, m tara A nengẽ somblelem sẽn yɩɩd wãnde"". La d na kõ kɩfr-rãmbã kɩbar ne bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmã, la D na leems-b naong sẽn tagme."
  41,51,"la Tõnd sã n maan ninsaal neema, a balldame n lɑk kɩrengɑ ne wɑoog-m-mengɑ, la wẽng sã n paam-a, la a sẽn yaa kos-yaleng soaba."
  41,52,"Yeele: ""yãmb yãame t'a (Alkʋrãɑnɑ) sã n yɩɩme n yi Wẽnd nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ tɩ yãmb kɩfl ne-a, ãnd meneng n yɩɩd ned ning sẽn welg n be zĩ-zãrgẽ?"""
  41,53,"D na n wilg-b-la d yel-soamã, ween-vɩɩsẽ wã la b mensẽ wã hal tɩ wa vẽneg ne bãmb t'a (Alkʋrãanã) yaa sɩda. Rẽ yĩngã pa sek tɩ fo Soabã yaa Seet ne bũmbã fãa gilli?"
  41,54,"Sɩdã, bãmbã bee sik pʋgẽ ne b Soabã sεgbo. Sɩdã, A yaa gũbgdɑ ne bũmbã fãa gilli."
